      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SILENT MINUTE (4) stuck on well last time to finish a nose back in second (22.91) at this track in a Grade 5 over 401m. Top chance in this line up. SURPRISE CHARGE (3) has been hard to follow lately, running fifth (18.64) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. Good beginner and aided by a handy draw. Expected to do much better this time. SIDE SHOW BOB (8) had a low draw latest where he found trouble and fell over 400m at Bulli. No luck latest and gets chance to atone. JAMES ALARM (7) was in the money last time at this track (22.83) in a Grade 5, finishing a 1.3 lengths second. Already a winner from this draw.",
